{"title":"alookso ─ 조소담","url":"https://alook.so/users/qQPtde","favicon":"https://alook.so/assets/favicon/favicon-32x32-8fc0ef8efcf005e31acc7291922e138cf3d3654531e4556566ca5cc4797a6793.png","elements":[{"title":"코로나 이후 근무 형태의 변화가 지역 발전에 영향을 미칠까요?","contents":"<div class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-gray-900\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-gray-900\">\n  <div class=\"relative mr-2\">\n      <a href=\"/users/qQPtde\"><img style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px;\" class=\"inline rounded-full object-cover border border-gray-200 bg-white \" src=\"https://alook.so/rails/active_storage/representations/redirect/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBZ29KIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--e562e2f4a53f50865d7664ade6d524212f8319d0/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaDdCem9MWm05eWJXRjBTU0lJYW5CbkJqb0dSVlE2RW5KbGMybDZaVjkwYjE5bWFYUmJCMmxGYVVVPSIsImV4cCI6bnVsbCwicHVyIjoidmFyaWF0aW9uIn19--e654fd14f4df7069a8a034146f678551e2aeda8b/IMG_1781.jpg\" width=\"32px\" height=\"32px\"></a>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"flex-1 leading-5\">\n    <div class=\"flex\">\n      <div class=\"text-xs flex\">\n          <a class=\"line-clamp-1 text-gray-400 whitespace-nowrap\" href=\"/users/qQPtde\">\n            <span class=\"text-gray-600 font-medium\">조소담</span>\n              <span class=\"text-xs text-gray-500\">\n                ·\n              </span>\n              <span class=\"break-all font-normal text-gray-400\">닷페이스</span>\n</a>      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"font-light text-gray-400 text-xxs\">\n      2021.10.08.\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n  \n</div>\n\n\n    <div class=\"flex-auto mt-2 space-y-2\">\n          <h5 class=\"font-medium text-break\" data-qa=\"post-title\">\n            <a class=\"text-xl text-gray-800 font-semibold line-clamp-2\" href=\"/posts/DjtaOr\">코로나 이후 근무 형태의 변화가 지역 발전에 영향을 미칠까요?</a>\n          </h5>\n\n        <h6 class=\"mb-2 font-normal text-gray-500\">\n    <a class=\"trix-content-post-partial line-clamp-5\" href=\"/posts/DjtaOr\">\n      <div class=\"trix-content\">\n          <span>오늘 본 좋은 기사를 공유합니다.\n<br>이 기사를 보다가 위 질문을 생각하게 됐는데요.&nbsp;</span><br>\n<br>\n<span>https://www.khan.co.kr/kh_storytelling/2021/graduate_country/?fbclid=IwAR0uui6pHOGQo88Qi3YxuHxiJ7eZOagWl-WRvu58wnX8PKWhlvCuf4zSww4</span><br>\n<br>\n<span>이 기사는 65명의 여성들이 어떻게 졸업 후 지역을 떠났는지,\n<br>각자 살던 곳의 미래를 어떻게 생각하는지 풀어주고 있어요.</span><br>\n<br>\n<span>지역으로 돌아오고 싶냐-는 질문에 많은 사람들이 '그렇다'라고 이야기하면서 붙인 조건, 두 가지가 제일 와닿네요.&nbsp; 첫번째는 일자리와 수입. 연봉을 서울에서보다 천만원 더 벌 수 있으면... 혹은 공무원,선생님 말고 일할 수 있는 일자리가 있다면 내려가겠다-라는 답변들이 중복되네요. 두번째는 교육에 대한 언급 등등..</span><br>\n<br>\n<span>그 중에 코로나에 대한 이야기가 나오는 게 인상 깊었어요.&nbsp;\n<br>코로나가 다시 고향으로 돌아갈 생각을 해보게 만드는 계...</span>\n      </div>\n</a></h6>\n\n\n          <div class=\"pt-1\">\n            <div class=\"space-y-2\">\n    <span class=\"inline-block\">\n      <button type=\"button\" class=\"flex items-center p-1 text-xs font-light text-gray-500 border border-gray-300 rounded\">\n        <a href=\"/topics/local\">\n          지방을 살릴 기회가 남아 있을까요?\n</a>      </button>\n    </span>\n</div>\n          </div>\n\n        <div class=\"flex justify-between pt-3 text-sm font-light text-gray-400\">\n          <span class=\"flex items-center\">\n            <a class=\"inline-block h-full whitespace-nowrap\" href=\"/posts/DjtaOr#reply\">\n              <svg class=\"inline-block -mr-0.5 mb-0.5 h-4 w-4 fill-current\"><use href=\"https://alook.so/assets/icons-980becba33ff5775625b73e0409369145b0da8c1df7bcfebf4430c8a8eb2a689.svg#icons-icon-line-reply\"></use></svg>\n                1\n</a>          </span>\n          <div class=\"flex items-center space-x-4\">\n            <div class=\"h-full whitespace-nowrap like_button_post_DjtaOr\">\n  <form class=\"button_to\" method=\"post\" action=\"/votes/like?toggle=up&amp;votable=BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSIbZ2lkOi8vYWxvb2sxL1Bvc3QvNDE5MAY7AFRJIgxwdXJwb3NlBjsAVEkiDGRlZmF1bHQGOwBUSSIPZXhwaXJlc19hdAY7AFRJIh0yMDIxLTExLTEzVDA1OjM4OjU5LjM4M1oGOwBU--4cc59464ca8e9e418af4a96fa7dc7c6525fe917f\"><button class=\"h-full whitespace-nowrap flex items-center\" type=\"submit\">\n    <svg class=\"inline-block mr-0.5 w-4 h-4 fill-current  \"><use href=\"https://alook.so/assets/icons-980becba33ff5775625b73e0409369145b0da8c1df7bcfebf4430c8a8eb2a689.svg#icons-icon-line-recommend\"></use></svg>\n    <span class=\"font-light \">\n      11\n    </span>\n</button><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"authenticity_token\" value=\"ZHnxA-3zeR8UAowrqTKM-5TDYnJ1TyDrfTJRlVvvtOexGZPf94HgqNhnvQGS5g36ufb12pSnR7ZN6M0SeTyPeA\"></form></div>\n            <div>\n  <div class=\"relative\">\n    <a tabindex=\"0\" class=\"inline-block select-none share_post_DjtaOr\" data-method=\"get\" href=\"/posts/DjtaOr/share\">\n      <svg class=\"h-4 w-4 fill-current\"><use href=\"https://alook.so/assets/icons-980becba33ff5775625b73e0409369145b0da8c1df7bcfebf4430c8a8eb2a689.svg#icons-icon-line-share\"></use></svg>\n</a>  </div>\n</div>\n\n          </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>","link":"https://alook.so/posts/DjtaOr","retrieved":1633651200000},{"title":"사회가 강요하는 모성에 대해서","contents":"<div class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-gray-900\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-gray-900\">\n  <div class=\"relative mr-2\">\n      <a href=\"/users/qQPtde\"><img style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px;\" class=\"inline rounded-full object-cover border border-gray-200 bg-white \" src=\"https://alook.so/rails/active_storage/representations/redirect/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBZ29KIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--e562e2f4a53f50865d7664ade6d524212f8319d0/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaDdCem9MWm05eWJXRjBTU0lJYW5CbkJqb0dSVlE2RW5KbGMybDZaVjkwYjE5bWFYUmJCMmxGYVVVPSIsImV4cCI6bnVsbCwicHVyIjoidmFyaWF0aW9uIn19--e654fd14f4df7069a8a034146f678551e2aeda8b/IMG_1781.jpg\" width=\"32px\" height=\"32px\"></a>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"flex-1 leading-5\">\n    <div class=\"flex\">\n      <div class=\"text-xs flex\">\n          <a class=\"line-clamp-1 text-gray-400 whitespace-nowrap\" href=\"/users/qQPtde\">\n            <span class=\"text-gray-600 font-medium\">조소담</span>\n              <span class=\"text-xs text-gray-500\">\n                ·\n              </span>\n              <span class=\"break-all font-normal text-gray-400\">닷페이스</span>\n</a>      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"font-light text-gray-400 text-xxs\">\n      2021.10.08.\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n  \n</div>\n\n\n    <div class=\"flex-auto mt-2 space-y-2\">\n          <h5 class=\"font-medium text-break\" data-qa=\"post-title\">\n            <a class=\"text-xl text-gray-800 font-semibold line-clamp-2\" href=\"/posts/rDtRr8\">사회가 강요하는 모성에 대해서 </a>\n          </h5>\n\n        <h6 class=\"mb-2 font-normal text-gray-500\">\n    <a class=\"trix-content-post-partial line-clamp-5\" href=\"/posts/rDtRr8\">\n      <div class=\"trix-content\">\n          <span>어제 오늘 이래저래 보게 된 기사, 게시글들이 이 질문과 연관된 것 같아 가져와봅니다. \n<br>이래저래 자꾸 '각서'쓰라고 하는 게 웃기다고도 생각했어요.</span><br>\n<br>\n<span>특히 주택 공급과 연계한 3의 사례는, 심각하게 여성의 재생산권을 침해하는 사례라고 생각했어요. \n<br>사회에 취약한 사람들을 위해 준비한 정책들이 이런 식으로 쓰이는 게 안타깝습니다.</span><br>\n<br>\n<span>'더 많은 아이를 낳아야 한다'라는 강요가 사회의 정책,제도 곳곳에 스며들 때 \n<br>여성의 재생산권이 어떻게 침해되는지&nbsp; 잘 감시하고 지켜봐야 한다고 생각해요. \n<br>&nbsp;</span><br>\n<br>\n<span>1.&nbsp; 보건소에 임산부 등록을 하러 갔다가 모유수유 서약이라는 걸 하라고 해서 동의하지 않는 내용이라 서명하지 않겠다 했다는 이야기&nbsp; \n<br>https://twitter.com/mayflyslayer/status/1445643871371751435?t=scsoYFRFxLuVLw0ZwG7wYw&amp;s=19</span><br>\n<br>\n<span>2. 남양 유업에서 임신 포기 각서 강제&nbsp; \n<br>https://www.hankyung...</span>\n      </div>\n</a></h6>\n\n\n          <div class=\"pt-1\">\n            <div class=\"space-y-2\">\n    <span class=\"inline-block\">\n      <button type=\"button\" class=\"flex items-center p-1 text-xs font-light text-gray-500 border border-gray-300 rounded\">\n        <a href=\"/topics/baby\">\n          아이, 갖고 싶으신가요?\n</a>      </button>\n    </span>\n</div>\n          </div>\n\n        <div class=\"flex justify-between pt-3 text-sm font-light text-gray-400\">\n          <span class=\"flex items-center\">\n            <a class=\"inline-block h-full whitespace-nowrap\" href=\"/posts/rDtRr8#reply\">\n              <svg class=\"inline-block -mr-0.5 mb-0.5 h-4 w-4 fill-current\"><use href=\"https://alook.so/assets/icons-980becba33ff5775625b73e0409369145b0da8c1df7bcfebf4430c8a8eb2a689.svg#icons-icon-line-reply\"></use></svg>\n                답글\n</a>          </span>\n          <div class=\"flex items-center space-x-4\">\n            <div class=\"h-full whitespace-nowrap like_button_post_rDtRr8\">\n  <form class=\"button_to\" method=\"post\" action=\"/votes/like?toggle=up&amp;votable=BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSIbZ2lkOi8vYWxvb2sxL1Bvc3QvNDE4NQY7AFRJIgxwdXJwb3NlBjsAVEkiDGRlZmF1bHQGOwBUSSIPZXhwaXJlc19hdAY7AFRJIh0yMDIxLTExLTEzVDA1OjM4OjU5LjM5MVoGOwBU--8b7163beb513ccbfd15f62647c8ab91a6a0f262c\"><button class=\"h-full whitespace-nowrap flex items-center\" type=\"submit\">\n    <svg class=\"inline-block mr-0.5 w-4 h-4 fill-current  \"><use href=\"https://alook.so/assets/icons-980becba33ff5775625b73e0409369145b0da8c1df7bcfebf4430c8a8eb2a689.svg#icons-icon-line-recommend\"></use></svg>\n    <span class=\"font-light \">\n      6\n    </span>\n</button><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"authenticity_token\" value=\"ZHnxA-3zeR8UAowrqTKM-5TDYnJ1TyDrfTJRlVvvtOexGZPf94HgqNhnvQGS5g36ufb12pSnR7ZN6M0SeTyPeA\"></form></div>\n            <div>\n  <div class=\"relative\">\n    <a tabindex=\"0\" class=\"inline-block select-none share_post_rDtRr8\" data-method=\"get\" href=\"/posts/rDtRr8/share\">\n      <svg class=\"h-4 w-4 fill-current\"><use href=\"https://alook.so/assets/icons-980becba33ff5775625b73e0409369145b0da8c1df7bcfebf4430c8a8eb2a689.svg#icons-icon-line-share\"></use></svg>\n</a>  </div>\n</div>\n\n          </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>","link":"https://alook.so/posts/rDtRr8","retrieved":1633651200000},{"title":"젊은 층의 자살률, 왜 늘었을까요?","contents":"<div class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-gray-900\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-gray-900\">\n  <div class=\"relative mr-2\">\n      <a href=\"/users/qQPtde\"><img style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px;\" class=\"inline rounded-full object-cover border border-gray-200 bg-white \" src=\"https://alook.so/rails/active_storage/representations/redirect/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBZ29KIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--e562e2f4a53f50865d7664ade6d524212f8319d0/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaDdCem9MWm05eWJXRjBTU0lJYW5CbkJqb0dSVlE2RW5KbGMybDZaVjkwYjE5bWFYUmJCMmxGYVVVPSIsImV4cCI6bnVsbCwicHVyIjoidmFyaWF0aW9uIn19--e654fd14f4df7069a8a034146f678551e2aeda8b/IMG_1781.jpg\" width=\"32px\" height=\"32px\"></a>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"flex-1 leading-5\">\n    <div class=\"flex\">\n      <div class=\"text-xs flex\">\n          <a class=\"line-clamp-1 text-gray-400 whitespace-nowrap\" href=\"/users/qQPtde\">\n            <span class=\"text-gray-600 font-medium\">조소담</span>\n              <span class=\"text-xs text-gray-500\">\n                ·\n              </span>\n              <span class=\"break-all font-normal text-gray-400\">닷페이스</span>\n</a>      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"font-light text-gray-400 text-xxs\">\n      2021.10.01.\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n  \n</div>\n\n\n    <div class=\"flex-auto mt-2 space-y-2\">\n          <h5 class=\"font-medium text-break\" data-qa=\"post-title\">\n            <a class=\"text-xl text-gray-800 font-semibold line-clamp-2\" href=\"/posts/6MtY0Y\">젊은 층의 자살률, 왜 늘었을까요? </a>\n          </h5>\n\n        <h6 class=\"mb-2 font-normal text-gray-500\">\n    <a class=\"trix-content-post-partial line-clamp-5\" href=\"/posts/6MtY0Y\">\n      <div class=\"trix-content\">\n          <span>요즘 저희 팀(닷페이스)에서는 젊은 층의 자살률이 화두가 되었었습니다.</span><br>\n<br>\n<span>얼마 전 9월 28일, 통계청에서 2020년 사망원인통계가 나왔는데요.</span><br>\n<br>\n<span>코로나19 사망자는 10만 명 당 1.9명, 자살 사망자는 25.7명이었습니다. \n<br>자살률은 전년 대비 10대는 9.4% 증가, 20대는 12.8%증가했다고 합니다. \n<br>특히 10대 남성의 자살률은 18.8%, 20대 여성의 자살률은 16.5% 늘었습니다.</span><br>\n<br>\n<span>국내에서 하루 평균 36명씩 자살을 하고, 전체 자살률이 줄었는데\n<br>10대-30대는 자살률이 늘었다는 점을 주목했어요.</span><br>\n<br>\n<span>주변에서도 우울증이 늘었다거나, 자살 시도한 지인이 있다는 이야기가 나왔습니다. \n<br>젊은 층의 자살률이 특히 증가한 이유가 뭐라고 생각하시나요?</span>\n      </div>\n</a></h6>\n\n\n          <div class=\"pt-1\">\n            <div class=\"space-y-2\">\n    <span class=\"inline-block\">\n      <button type=\"button\" class=\"flex items-center p-1 text-xs font-light text-gray-500 border border-gray-300 rounded\">\n        <a href=\"/topics/open\">\n          새로운 질문을 던져주세요.\n</a>      </button>\n    </span>\n    <span class=\"inline-block\">\n      <button type=\"button\" class=\"flex items-center p-1 text-xs font-light text-gray-500 border border-gray-300 rounded\">\n        <a href=\"/topics/koreanteenager\">\n          한국의 10대는 왜 불행한가요?\n</a>      </button>\n    </span>\n</div>\n          </div>\n\n        <div class=\"flex justify-between pt-3 text-sm font-light text-gray-400\">\n          <span class=\"flex items-center\">\n            <a class=\"inline-block h-full whitespace-nowrap\" href=\"/posts/6MtY0Y#reply\">\n              <svg class=\"inline-block -mr-0.5 mb-0.5 h-4 w-4 fill-current\"><use href=\"https://alook.so/assets/icons-980becba33ff5775625b73e0409369145b0da8c1df7bcfebf4430c8a8eb2a689.svg#icons-icon-line-reply\"></use></svg>\n                3\n</a>          </span>\n          <div class=\"flex items-center space-x-4\">\n            <div class=\"h-full whitespace-nowrap like_button_post_6MtY0Y\">\n  <form class=\"button_to\" method=\"post\" action=\"/votes/like?toggle=up&amp;votable=BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSIbZ2lkOi8vYWxvb2sxL1Bvc3QvMTkzNwY7AFRJIgxwdXJwb3NlBjsAVEkiDGRlZmF1bHQGOwBUSSIPZXhwaXJlc19hdAY7AFRJIh0yMDIxLTExLTEzVDA1OjM4OjU5LjQxM1oGOwBU--f29a95e83401e1118d95cd9c1ce13224c751f072\"><button class=\"h-full whitespace-nowrap flex items-center\" type=\"submit\">\n    <svg class=\"inline-block mr-0.5 w-4 h-4 fill-current  \"><use href=\"https://alook.so/assets/icons-980becba33ff5775625b73e0409369145b0da8c1df7bcfebf4430c8a8eb2a689.svg#icons